{"tid":1872170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特衰政府停擺？","createTime":"2020-02-10T02:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T03:22:20.000Z","uid":117634,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce27da58bdfe5ae087ce0a80ce947842b8effaf","tid":1872170,"uid":117634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"P牌夠一年今日終於可以去換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網check過今日只做預約<br />\n但個牌夠左期上網唔比預約<br />\n今日一早去沙田TD博一博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDKLM開都唔開<br />\n派左2個實Q出黎講今日唔開<br />\n一個職員都無，實q們比人屌到反皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人一早黎排<br />\n行車証到期又有<br />\n申請國際牌又有<br />\n淨係得4個藍箱放門口比人遞form<br />\n實q們就撲左d信封比人交文件<br />\n粗口聲此起彼落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳說中10號真係真收皮唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係未連投遞都唔會搞？<br />\n<br />\n好啦。<br />\n依家車又揸唔到要迫19港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果揸出去又會比黑狗捉重考都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問各位巴絲有無人同我一樣<br />\n比我圍爐取下暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8iT0Sd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8iT0Sd.png&h=df9f182d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終決定原來要留意林奠的公佈 (實q話)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBvSwYZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBvSwYZ.png&h=3b343290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲安排都做得咁差<br />\n個政府真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7905dd8f4299d821f1c8054e66ae676ac93f01d","tid":1872170,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"開咗56789 五日咁大把"},{"pid":"d624dc306b5af184dc1cbac358c95e7a27610d22","tid":1872170,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":